snippet.title: RPG Fanatic Earth - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Expose and bring down a corporate giant!
RPG Fanatic Earth is now available for Android!

Get it now on:

Google Play
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=kemco.execreate.fearth&hl=en

Xilleon City- a massive dome metropolis that protects those living beneath its shield from a deadly alien bacteria. Among its residents is a man by the name of Zech, who, after thwarting an attack by local gang members, finds himself on the radar of Cyphatek- a large conglomerate with virtually unlimited influence in the city. Not one to run from a fight, Zech storms their private club, but what is it he discovers?!
Become a defender of justice in this new sci-fi fantasy RPG and find out!

©2013-2014 KEMCO/EXE-CREATE
※All graphics terms, characters and elements are subject to change in the actual product.
